Running tests

.. code:: shell

  $ git clone git@github.com:pior/buddy.git
  ...
  $ mkvirtualenv buddy -p python3
  ...
  $ pip install -U -r requirements-test.txt
  ...
  $ pip install -e .
  ...
  $ pytest


